General.Name: Mepet Metro Petrol ve Tesisleri Sanayi Ticaret AS
General.Description: Mepet Metro Petrol ve Tesisleri Sanayi Ticaret A.S. owns and operates fuel stations and road rest facilities in Turkey. The company owns and operates 24 fuel stations that sell fuel and petroleum products. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Beykoz, Turkey.
